==Usage==
To collect images or [[Template/en/Userbox]]es into a single column grouping easily

<pre>
{{userboxtop}}
[userboxes]
{{userboxbottom}}
</pre>

userboxtop Parameters (All of the parameters are '''optional'''):
<pre>{{userboxtop
| align           = left|right (default = right)
| left            = left margin value(default = 1)
| backgroundcolor = background color (default = #FFFFFF)
| bordercolor     = border color (default = #99B3FF)
| extra-css       = other parameter (CSS)
| textcolor       = text color (default = #000000)
| toptext         = Overrides the standard Userbox text and link. Can include wiki-markup
}}
</pre>

